{The Portsmouth Road Area { Most of the houses are about 50 years old.Four were old Victorian houses (terraced) and two ten year old flats. 2 people were born here,5 houses where we enquired were owner-occupied.Two of these people wanted to move house.The average time for living there was 37 years.
